</td><td width="174" valign="top" colspan="1" rowspan="1">年度制作</td><td width="76" valign="top" colspan="1" class="coloredcell"><b>获奖</b></td></tr><tr><td width="170" valign="top" colspan="1" rowspan="1">2006年5月23日</td><td width="237" valign="top" colspan="1" rowspan="1">美国版权协会流行奖<sup>[17]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[17]_14427351">&nbsp;</a>
</td><td width="174" valign="top" colspan="1" rowspan="1">年度最佳歌曲</td><td width="76" valign="top" colspan="1" class="coloredcell"><b>获奖</b></td></tr><tr><td width="170" valign="top">2006年5月27日</td><td width="237" valign="top">日本MTV音乐视频奖<sup>[18]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[18]_14427351">&nbsp;</a>
</td><td width="174" valign="top">最佳摇滚视频</td><td width="76" valign="top" colspan="1" class="coloredcell"><b>获奖</b></td></tr></table><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="6" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub14427351_6" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="重要演出" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">Boulevard Of Broken Dreams</span>重要演出</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="6" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<table log-set-param="table_view" class="table-view log-set-param" width="658"><tr><th width="173">日期</th><th width="292">演出场合</th><th width="192">地点</th></tr><tr><td width="173" valign="top"><div class="para" label-module="para">2005年8月28日</div>
</td><td width="292" valign="top"><div class="para" label-module="para">MTV音乐录影带奖颁奖典礼<sup>[3]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[3]_14427351">&nbsp;</a>
</div>
</td><td width="192" valign="top"><div class="para" label-module="para">迈阿密美航体育馆</div>
</td></tr></table><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="7" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub14427351_7" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="发行信息" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">Boulevard Of Broken Dreams</span>发行信息</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="7" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">在美国的公告牌数字下载单曲榜上，《Boulevard of Broken Dreams》依靠三万一千张的音乐销量夺得排行榜冠军<sup>[19]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[19]_14427351">&nbsp;</a>
。</div>
<div class="anchor-list">
<a name="a" class="lemma-anchor a" ></a>
</div><div class="album-list">
